{"ja450:0.1":"Jataka ","ja450:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja450:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja450:0.4":"12. Bilarakosiyajataka ","ja450:1.1":"“Apacantapi dicchanti, ","ja450:1.2":"santo laddhana bhojanam; ","ja450:1.3":"Kimeva tvam pacamano, ","ja450:1.4":"yam na dajja na tam samam. ","ja450:2.1":"Macchera ca pamada ca, ","ja450:2.2":"evam danam na diyyati; ","ja450:2.3":"Punnam akankhamanena, ","ja450:2.4":"deyyam hoti vijanata. ","ja450:3.1":"Yasseva bhito na dadati macchari, ","ja450:3.2":"Tadevadadato bhayam; ","ja450:3.3":"Jighaccha ca pipasa ca, ","ja450:3.4":"Yassa bhayati macchari; ","ja450:3.5":"Tameva balam phusati, ","ja450:3.6":"Asmim loke paramhi ca. ","ja450:4.1":"Tasma vineyya maccheram, ","ja450:4.2":"dajja danam malabhibhu; ","ja450:4.3":"Punnani paralokasmim, ","ja450:4.4":"patittha honti paninam”. ","ja450:5.1":"“Duddadam dadamananam, ","ja450:5.2":"dukkaram kamma kubbatam; ","ja450:5.3":"Asanto nanukubbanti, ","ja450:5.4":"satam dhammo durannayo. ","ja450:6.1":"Tasma satanca asatam, ","ja450:6.2":"nana hoti ito gati; ","ja450:6.3":"Asanto nirayam yanti, ","ja450:6.4":"santo saggaparayana”. ","ja450:7.1":"“Appasmeke pavecchanti, ","ja450:7.2":"bahuneke na dicchare; ","ja450:7.3":"Appasma dakkhina dinna, ","ja450:7.4":"sahassena samam mita”. ","ja450:8.1":"“Dhammam care yopi samunchakam care, ","ja450:8.2":"Daranca posam dadamappakasmim; ","ja450:8.3":"Satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","ja450:8.4":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”. ","ja450:9.1":"“Kenesa yanno vipulo mahagghato, ","ja450:9.2":"Samena dinnassa na agghameti; ","ja450:9.3":"Katham satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","ja450:9.4":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”. ","ja450:10.1":"“Dadanti heke visame nivittha, ","ja450:10.2":"Chetva vadhitva atha socayitva; ","ja450:10.3":"Sa dakkhina assumukha sadanda, ","ja450:10.4":"Samena dinnassa na agghameti; ","ja450:10.5":"Evam satam sahassanam sahassayaginam, ","ja450:10.6":"Kalampi nagghanti tathavidhassa te”ti. ","ja450:11.1":"Bilarakosiyajatakam dvadasamam. "}